      <title>特朗普团队难以削弱卡马拉·哈里斯的势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-2024-campaign-against-kamala-harris-is-fighting-her-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的总统竞选活动突然开始迎头赶上，自副总统加入竞选以来，他一直在竞相寻找方法来削弱卡玛拉·哈里斯背后的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-2024-campaign-against-kamala-harris-is-fighting-her-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在新一轮救助之前通知学生贷款借款人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-to-notify-borrowers-before-new-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 11 月总统大选临近之际，总统乔·拜登的政府通知数百万可能有资格获得贷款减免的美国人，提醒选民关注期待已久的学生债务减免计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-to-notify-borrowers-before-new-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将与中国官员举行新一轮芬太尼管制谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-will-host-chinese-officials-for-new-talks-on-curbing-fentanyl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将接待由中国高级官员组成的代表团，就遏制芬太尼流动进行新一轮会谈，这是拜登总统政府为解决已成为 2024 年大选问题之一的阿片类药物危机所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-will-host-chinese-officials-for-new-talks-on-curbing-fentanyl</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军政府再次延长紧急状态 内战愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/myanmar-junta-extends-emergency-rule-again-as-civil-war-rages-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政权延长了自 2021 年政变以来实施的紧急状态，因为将军们正努力平息与少数民族武装团体和民主战士的内战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/myanmar-junta-extends-emergency-rule-again-as-civil-war-rages-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:49:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯给出迄今为止最明确的信号，她将在预算中提高英国税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/reeves-gives-clearest-sign-yet-she-will-raise-uk-taxes-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）给出了迄今为止最明确的信号，她准备在十月份的首份英国预算中提高税收，以填补公共账户中 164 亿英镑（210 亿美元）的黑洞，她表示这是她从上届保守党政府那里继承下来的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/reeves-gives-clearest-sign-yet-she-will-raise-uk-taxes-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:26:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯战争损失不断增加，普京将军队招募奖金增加一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/putin-doubles-army-recruitment-bonus-as-russian-war-losses-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令官员对愿意参加俄罗斯在乌克兰战争的人员给予双倍奖金，这再次证明军队难以达到招募目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/putin-doubles-army-recruitment-bonus-as-russian-war-losses-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:17:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉丁美洲可能错失美联储进一步降息的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latin-america-risks-squandering-rate-cut-opportunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当美联储似乎准备为拉丁美洲各国央行继续降息铺平道路时，这些国家国内日益严重的政治问题势必会扰乱——甚至逆转——这些宽松政策的实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latin-america-risks-squandering-rate-cut-opportunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体称苏丹领导人躲过无人机袭击，造成五人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/sudanese-leader-survives-drone-attack-on-army-camp-media-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据阿拉伯媒体报道，苏丹军事领导人阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·布尔汉躲过了一次无人机对军营的袭击，此次袭击造成 5 人死亡，这加剧了该国持续一年多的内战的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/sudanese-leader-survives-drone-attack-on-army-camp-media-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:56:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅遭遇今年最大夜间无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kyiv-suffers-biggest-overnight-drone-attack-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰首都基辅军事管理局称，该市成为今年迄今为止最大规模的俄罗斯无人机袭击的目标，袭击持续了几乎一整夜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kyiv-suffers-biggest-overnight-drone-attack-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:34:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚最大州政府争取自治权 收回天然气资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/malaysia-s-biggest-state-carves-out-gas-assets-in-autonomy-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚最大的州砂拉越将从联邦政府运营的公司手中接管其天然气资产的控制权，该州争取经济自治的运动在该东南亚国家脆弱的政治局势中取得了成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/malaysia-s-biggest-state-carves-out-gas-assets-in-autonomy-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
